instructions: Put the charger underneath the plate
Put the Napkin vertically on top of the Plate
Put the Dinner Fork to the left of the Charger facing upward
Put the Salad Fork to the left of the Dinner Fork
Put the Dinner Knife to the right of the Charger
Put the Tea Spoon to the right of the Dinner Knife
Put the Soup Spoon to the right of the Tea Spoon
Put the Water Glass to the right above the Charger and Dinner Knife
Put the Wine Glass to the right of the Water Glass
Put the Wine Glass diagonal to the Water Glass
Put the Coffee Cup to the right of the Wine Glass and Soup Spoon
Put the Bread Plate diagonal to the Charger
Put the Butter Knife on top of the Bread Plate with the blade facing the horizontally to the left
Put the Dessert Fork above the Charger with the tines facing the Water Glass
Put the Dessert Spoon between the Dessert Fork and the Charger with the bowl facing the Bread Plate
